<div class="row">
  <div class="col s12 m9 hero-unit">
      <div class="white-text main-image">
        <h1 class="center-align"><span class="text-white">Welcome to Glass Basement</span></h1>
        <div class="center-align">
          <p class="flow-text">This site is dedicated to helping Turing Students as they go through the interview process.</p>
          <p class="flow-text">A crowsourced interview database containing the information gathered from successful and less successful interviews. As Turing Students interview, they can record their experience interviewing with that company. What company, what type of interview, what did the company ask, who did you interview with,  etc..</p>
          <p class="flow-text">Current students interviewing can look at past interviews, as well as access a chat room for any additional information they may want to receive from past interviewees.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="center-align">
          <% unless current_user %>
            <a class="btn btn-large  amber" href="/auth/github">Login to Get Started</a>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>
  </div>
</div>